      "content": "i rly dont think they understand. every time i'm around, i just bring this heavy energy... i feel like a poison. i keep thinking that if i just stepped out of the picture, the weight would lift and they could finally breathe. wouldn't it be more unselfish to just... let them be happy without me?",
